# Markdown Bibles — Repository License

This repository contains multiple Bible translations, each with their own license:

## Translations

| Translation | License | Location |
|------------|---------|----------|
| BSB (Berean Standard Bible) | CC BY-SA 4.0 | [bsb/LICENSE](bsb/LICENSE) |

## General

Each Bible translation folder contains its own license file. Please respect the license terms of each translation.

For the BSB specifically, see [bsb/LICENSE](bsb/LICENSE).

## About This Repository

A collection of Bible translations in Markdown format, freely available for AI agent platforms like OpenClaw and Hermes.
